        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">CEC-accredited solar panel &amp; battery installers serving Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes and the wider Cardinia Shire. Tier-1 solar PV, Tesla Powerwall &amp; battery storage, EV chargers, solar repairs. Cheaper Home Batteries rebate, Solar Victoria &amp; STCs applied. United Energy approved.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${PHONE_TEL}`}>{PHONE_DISPLAY}</a></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Hours:</strong> Mon&ndash;Sat 7am&ndash;6pm</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Service area:</strong> Pakenham VIC 3810 &amp; Cardinia Shire</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong style="color:#fff;">ABN:</strong> 91 664 546 061</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Services</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/services/solar-panel-installation/">Solar panel installation</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/battery-storage/">Battery storage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/solar-battery-systems/">Solar + battery systems</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/ev-charger-installation/">EV charger installation</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/solar-repairs-servicing/">Solar repairs &amp; servicing</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Service Areas</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/officer/">Officer</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a></li>
          <li><a href="/lakeside/">Lakeside</a></li>
          <li><a href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a></li>
